# Keep the build context small and secret-free.
# Only apps/cms + apps/clay are built. apps/web is NOT built — but its
# package.json manifest is still needed so `pnpm install --frozen-lockfile`
# matches the workspace lockfile, so we exclude web's SOURCE and keep the manifest.

# --- deps / build artifacts (regenerated in-image) ---
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/dist
**/coverage

# --- vcs / ci / editor ---
.git
.github
**/.claude
**/.DS_Store
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
*.bundle

# --- secrets (never ship into an image) ---
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# --- heavy, build-irrelevant content ---
# 600MB+ of source handoff material — not needed to build cms/clay.
handoff
docs
scratchpad
*.md

# --- apps/web: not built. Drop its source, keep only the manifest. ---
apps/web/**
!apps/web/package.json
